The Castle courtyard
Your currently in castles courtyard. Its a lot more peacful than the hustle and bustle of the city streets, with only couple of guards and a few nobles walking about. The courtyard also has a lush garden which adds nicely to the scenery.
You can see a Guard and Gregory.
You can go east or west.
> speak to gregory

> speak to gregory

"Oh you good, you came. Now before we can go on our little quest, you need to first talk to the King. "

"He's right through the doors that lead lead to the Throne room. But it's blocked by that guard; who wont allow anyone in. I told him about our meeting with the King but he didn't believe me. He then told me to go suck a lemon. Maybe you should try talking to him."

> speak to guard

> speak to guard

As your about to talk to the guard he rudely interrupts you.

"Look pal the throne room is off limits as the king is busy with an important matter.

The guard pokes you in the chest with his stern finger.

"So how about you do me a favor and take you'r pedohile wizard friend and f@#$ off!"

> give cute kitty cat to guard

> give cute kitty cat to guard

You give the Cute kitty cat to the borthersome guard in hopes that he'll let you into the throne room.
The guard glares at you and say's.

"You think that I'll let you through after giving me a cat?"

The cat lets out a cute "Meow", which the guard notices.

"Well it's a really cute cat. Okay maybe I'll let you through this one  time. But after give the cat a little pet."

The guard reaches his hand down to pet the Cute kitty cat. The instant his hand touches it, the cat let's out a horrifying hiss.

The cat then pounces on the guards face and claws at him.

"ARGH GET IT OFF ME!" he yells as he flails around on the ground in pain,

Blood spurts in every direction as the cat furiously claws the guard to death. The guard tries to smacking the cat off his face and head butting into the ground, but to no avail.

After several frighting minutes, the screams of the guard stops. You see the guard's body remain motionless as the cat still continues to claw away at the guard.

Afterwards the once Cute kitty cat, now blood soaked realizes that the guard is most likely dead and runs off out the castle gate.

You stand there traumatized, trying to make sense of what just happend before snapping out of it minutes later.

Well atleast the Throne room is now open.

