The Grand throne room
You enter the castle hall where the king sits ontop of his mighty throne, which is adorned various gems and elaborate fabrics. The hallway is also adorned with banners, tapestry and a long purple carpet that leads to the throne.
You can see a King Biggus Dickus.
You can go east.
> speak to king

> speak to king

'Ah! Another adventurer. I'm guessing that your here for the quest to slay the dragon. Am I correct?'

You nod.

"That's good. Ever since that Dragon made the mountain it's new home, it has caused all sorts of trouble. livestock has been eaten, villages have been burned and to top it off and to top it off, the Cheese Wheel Factory has been destroyed. WHERE WILL WE GET OUR CHEESE WHEELS NOW!"

You see a single tear roll down the Kings eye.

"Ehem, excuse me. I just really like cheese wheels."

He quiclky wipes his face and continues on.

"Ever since the Band of Heroes were defeated by the Dragon, the well bieng of the kingdom is looking more grim. I've been sending numerouse amount adventures, heroes and mercenary's in an effort to defeat it, but alas, none of them were successful. At this point, I'll except anyone willing to fight the dragon. So I give you my blessing and the quest to defeat the Dragon."

The King gives you his blessing and sends you out of the castle.

